metadata.name: MOE X NLCH Legendary Waifu Edition
metadata.description:
Legendary 1/1 waifu artwork collaboration by NLCH, a very popular illustrator known for his cute & eechi waifus. Mio is an original character designed with love by NLCH. 

Artwork Information:

In Tachibana town , there lived a samurai princess, grace and strength to which no one compares. She was admired by all that lived during her time not just because of her beauty, but also because of her using Karasuba the legendary katana killed a demon tiger. She wears a kimono with Sakura prints in honor of the Eastmost land where she was born. The cheerful beaut was Mio.

Artist information :

NLCH is a very popular illustrator known for his cute & eechi waifus. Proceeds from the artwork will be split to NLCH and MOE Anime fund, to support more aspiring anime artists in Metaverse üê±
